    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "the silence sounds so much better than this. i look at everything i've lost and it just makes so much sense that it's over. there's no version of the future where i'm not just exhausted and disappointed again. it feels like the only way to actually get that peace you're talking about... that real silence... is to just stop everything. to just let go completely so I don't have to feel this pressure anymore.",
